{"_path":"/construction/c06","_dir":"construction","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"順達科技樂善科技園區建廠","description":null,"image":"/images/construction/c06-1.jpeg","sequence":6,"category":"工商發展","status":"2.施工","type":"green","budget":null,"link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"順達科技樂善科技園區建廠"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"順達科技樂善科技園區建廠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"計畫概要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫概要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 順達科技樂善科技園區建廠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"類別 工商發展 - CON-06"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完工 2025"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"狀態 施工"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"順達二廠, 辦公室興建中, 網路猜測 2024~2025 有公司進駐"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"建設詳情"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建設詳情"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善科學園區開發\n樂善科學園區加上華亞科技園區，產值將達竹科的一半，要打造成桃園版的內湖科技園區，同時「亞洲•矽谷計劃」也會將此處作為重要的實驗場及推動產官學合作方案的基地。產業專區 45 公頃，22 公頃由禾聯碩標得；另一半的土地由中華郵政公司設置物流中心及行政大樓，中華郵政未來的營運重心將會移至本區。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c05-1.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c05-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"順達,致茂與禾聯碩廠區\n樂善科技園區將是桃園版內湖科學園區。該區已由順達科技、致茂電子及禾揚國際（禾聯）等 3 家民間企業標下 22.23 公頃土地，其中致茂與禾聯碩各 35%土地，順達科則取得 30%土地。致茂電子預計設立新總部及生產基地，順達科技則做為新總部、研發、生產基地，禾聯碩則設定為電視、節能空調等產品的第 2 生產據點，3 家預計共創造 2300 個以上的就業機會，年產值將達到 1100 億元。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"順達科技樂善科技園區建廠","depth":2,"text":"順達科技樂善科技園區建廠","children":[{"id":"計畫概要","depth":3,"text":"計畫概要"},{"id":"建設詳情","depth":3,"text":"建設詳情"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:construction:c06.md","_source":"content","_file":"construction/c06.md","_extension":"md"}